{"word":"ῥόμβος","slug":"ῥόμβος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n92685\" key=\"r(o/mbos\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ῥόμβος</orth> or <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ῥύμβος</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ῥέμβω</etym>) <sense id=\"n92685.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">bull-roarer</tr_>, instrument whirled round on the end of a string, used in the mysteries, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ῥόμβου θ᾽ εἱλισσομένα κύκλιος ἔνοσις αἰθερία</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg014.perseus-grc1:1362\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hel.\">Hel.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1362</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0620.tlg001:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Archyt.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:30\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Theoc.\">Theoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.30</biblScope> </bibl>; as a boy's toy, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">AP</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.309</biblScope> </bibl> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Leon.\">Leon.</a></author> </bibl>), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0579.tlg011:31:29\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Orph.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope